Quote:  <i>KATHETOSTOMA GIGANTEUM</i> Haast.  Flathead. Common, North Auckland Peninsula; but seldom utilized as a food fish. Occasionally seen in Christchurch markets. Distribution: New Zealand coasts (rarer in the extreme south).
Notes:  Phillipps Notes on the Edible Fishes

